      "text": "🛡️ Two-Stage Scam Detection Pipeline",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "scam-v1-ref",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 25,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "V1 Cross-Ref: Section 5.1 (Scam), 9.1 → AD-12",
      "strokeColor": "#845ef7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontStyle": "italic"
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1a-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#b2f2bb",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1a-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 215,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "📱 Layer 1a: Edge (On-Device)",
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1a-text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 610,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "⚡ Performance: <100ms, zero network\n\n3 Input Corpora:\n1️⃣ URL/Domain Blocklist: Phishing domains, fraudulent UPI handles → silent sync\n2️⃣ Indic Keywords: Financial urgency in 12 languages: \"transfer now\", \"account blocked\", \"send OTP\"\n3️⃣ Structural Patterns: \"Hi Mummy/Papa, phone broke\" → regex-resistant to variation\n\nAction: Quarantine → Encrypted buffer + Caregiver alert\nTimeline: G-01: 5-7 weeks (corpus curation = critical path)",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1b-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 770,
      "y": 195,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1b-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 215,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "☁️ Layer 1b: Semantic (Cloud)",
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "layer1b-text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 250,
      "width": 610,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "⚡ Performance: ~2s latency (acceptable)\n\nTrigger: Messages passing Layer 1a with ambiguous signals\n\nClaude Haiku 4.5 + scam-classification system prompt\n   Structured JSON (PydanticAI validated)\n   Input: Message + sender status + last 3 turns\n   Output: Threat score (0-1), category, explanation\n\nTarget: Friend-in-distress, emotional manipulation,\n   data extraction, authority impersonation\n\nCost: $0.08/user/month (40 msg/day)",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "lime-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 415,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#20c997",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#d3f9d8",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "lime-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 435,
      "width": 550,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "🔍 LIME Attribution: Explainable Alerts",
      "strokeColor": "#087f5b",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "lime-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 470,
      "width": 610,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Problem: Classifier returns \"0.87\" → caregiver can't act\n\nSolution: LIME generates feature-level attribution\n   Identifies specific phrases/patterns driving score\n\nCaregiver Alert Example:\n\"A message from an unknown number was blocked.\nIt claimed to be from Rajan and asked Meena to\nsend ₹5,000 urgently. This is a common fraud pattern.\"\n\nCaregiver Action: Approve (release) or Confirm Block\n   Confirm → adds pattern to edge filter corpus\n\nCost: $0.01/user/month (5 events/month)",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "prompt-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 770,
      "y": 415,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffe3e3",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "prompt-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 435,
      "width": 550,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "🛡️ Prompt Injection Prevention",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "prompt-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 470,
      "width": 610,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Attack: Hidden instructions in forwarded content\n   (news article, recipe) → overrides safety behaviours\n\nMitigation 1: System Prompt Pinning (Model-level)\n   SOUL.md at highest trust → content in user turns = untrusted DATA\n   Leverages: Sonnet 4.6 prompt-injection resistance\n\nMitigation 2: Content Boundary Marking (Architecture)\n   XML-style tags for externally sourced content\n   Output validation: Unapproved phones, financial accounts,\n   software downloads",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "healthcare-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 640,
      "width": 700,
      "height": 35,
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "🏥 Healthcare: ABDM + FHIR + DPDP Compliance",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "healthcare-v1-ref",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 680,
      "width": 450,
      "height": 25,
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "V1 Cross-Ref: Section 5.3 (DPDP), 9.1 → AD-13",
      "strokeColor": "#845ef7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontStyle": "italic"
    },
    {
      "id": "abdm-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 715,
      "width": 1400,
      "height": 180,
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#d0ebff",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "abdm-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 735,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "📋 ABDM Framework Roles + Compliance Proxy Flow",
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "abdm-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 770,
      "width": 1350,
      "height": 110,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "ABDM Roles: HIP (Hospital/Clinic- NOT our role) | HIU (Our role: requests health records) | Health Locker (Consent manager)\n\nCompliance Proxy 7-Step Flow:\n1. Healthcare Provider initiates request → 2. Proxy initiates ABDM consent handshake → 3. Elder sees plain-language consent (\"Dr. Sharma wants test reports. Agree?\")\n4. On confirmation → consent artefact to Health Locker → 5. Health Locker routes to relevant HIP → 6. Proxy validates FHIR, extracts to narrative (NOT raw FHIR)\n   → 7. Narrative injected to LLM (raw FHIR encrypted, scrubbed on session)\n\nWhy no raw FHIR: SNOMED/LOINC codes → hallucination risk (clinically unacceptable)\nTimeline: G-08: 11-14 weeks (+ABDM enrolment +BODH)",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "bodh-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 915,
      "width": 650,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffe3e3",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "bodh-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 935,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "🆕 G-NEW-03: BODH Clinical (Phase 2 BLOCKER)",
      "strokeColor": "#c92a2a",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "bodh-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 120,
      "y": 970,
      "width": 610,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "BODH: India's framework for health AI validation\n\n4 Mandatory Dimensions (ALL required for Phase 2):\n\n1️⃣ Diagnostic Accuracy: Zero safety omissions,\n   zero hallucinated clinical values\n\n2️⃣ Algorithmic Fairness: Disaggregated across\n   demographics (age, gender, urban/rural)\n\n3️⃣ Clinical Safety Matrix: ANY failure = release\n   blocker (drug names, dosage, allergies)\n\n4️⃣ Regional Language Accuracy: Readability +\n   clinical accuracy together\n\nTimeline: 4-6 weeks | Next: Submit BODH access",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "dpdp-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 770,
      "y": 915,
      "width": 730,
      "height": 200,
      "strokeColor": "#845ef7",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "#e5dbff",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "roundness": {"type": 2, "value": 8}
    },
    {
      "id": "dpdp-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 935,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "🔐 DPDP Act 2023 Implementation",
      "strokeColor": "#7950f2",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "dpdp-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 790,
      "y": 970,
      "width": 690,
      "height": 130,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "1️⃣ Verifiable Consent: Immutable ledger per data category\n   (conversation, health, financial, caregiver visibility)\n   Plain-language, cryptographic hash, withdrawal mechanism\n\n2️⃣ Data Minimisation: Only necessary fields injected\n   (Temporal + PydanticAI enforce at activity level)\n\n3️⃣ Right to Erasure: Cascading delete (72-hour window)\n   Qdrant: Delete vectors → tombstone\n   PostgreSQL: Drop health partition → re-create empty\n   Device: Push notification wipes cache\n   LLM API: Submit deletion via Anthropic\n   Certificate: Signed JSON commitment",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "cost-title",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1140,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 35,
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "💰 V2 Full Stack Cost (9 Line Items)",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontWeight": "bold"
    },
    {
      "id": "cost-table",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1180,
      "width": 1400,
      "height": 250,
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "Component | Technology | Monthly Cost | Notes\n------------------------------------------------------------\n1. Core inference | Claude Sonnet 4.6 | $3.60 | 15 msg/day @ blended context\n2. Scam L1a (edge) | On-device | $0.00 | Zero inference, amortized\n3. Scam L1b (semantic) | Claude Haiku 4.5 | $0.08 | 40 msg/day @ 200 tokens\n4. Readability | AI4Bharat NLP self-hosted | $0.04 | Morphological analyzer\n5. Simplification | Claude Haiku 4.5 | $0.03 | 30% of responses triggered\n6. Temporal.io | Temporal Cloud | $0.12 | ~200 workflow actions\n7. LIME attribution | Claude Haiku 4.5 | $0.01 | 5 scam events/month\n8. Context summarization | Claude Haiku 4.5 | $0.02 | 4×/month (unchanged)\n9. IndicConformer | CDN updates | $0.02 | Model amortized\n------------------------------------------------------------\nTOTAL: $3.92/user/month (+$0.21 over V1 $3.71)\n✅ Still UNDER $5.00 Phase 1 viability threshold",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    {
      "id": "validation-note",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 100,
      "y": 1450,
      "width": 1400,
      "height": 30,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "All 3 V2 diagrams include: Balanced emphasis · Specific timelines (week estimates) · V1 cross-references · Consistent color scheme · No text overlap",
      "strokeColor": "#666666",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    }
